*Nebo* je plavo kao more. (The sky is blue as the sea.)

*Nebom* je prekrio oblake. (He covered the sky with clouds.)

Pogledajmo prema *nebu*. (Let's look up to the sky.)

Planina seže do *neba*. (The mountain reaches the sky.)

Na *nebu* se vide zvezde. (You can see stars in the sky.)

Gradovi su se pružili do *neba*. (The cities stretched up to the sky.)